        <div class="row">
           <div class="col-lg-7 m-auto py-5 text-justify">


            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12">
                    <h2>About Us</h2>
                    <p>At Shoe Haven, we're not just another footwear store; we're an independently-owned small and medium-sized enterprise (SME) that's passionate about bringing quality and style to your feet. Our journey began with a simple idea: to provide our community with a haven for shoes that combine comfort and fashion effortlessly.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="col-12">
                    <h4>Our Mission:</h4>
                    <p>Our mission is to elevate your style, one step at a time, by offering affordable, high-quality footwear that doesn't compromise on style. We aim to empower individuals to express themselves through their choice of footwear and help them stride confidently on every path they choose.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="col-12">
                    <h4>Our Vision:</h4>
                    <p>We envision a world where everyone has access to comfortable, stylish footwear that reflects their unique tastes and preferences. Shoe Haven aims to be the go-to destination for individuals seeking both classic and cutting-edge designs, ensuring their every step is a statement of fashion and comfort.</p>
                </div>

            </div>

           </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

